als and other items she took delivery three weeks ago for the Bakassi displaced people. June 15, 2017 In "News" CALABAR—CROSS River State House of Assembly Committee investigating allegations of diversion of relief materials is to summon Senator Florence Ita-Giwa and other Bakassi leaders to give details of how materials supplied to the Internally Displaced Persons, IDP, in Bakassi were distributed. June 16, 2017 In "News"